1
00:00:00,426 --> 00:00:04,950
♪A little bit sorry for my love for you♪

2
00:00:04,950 --> 00:00:10,454
♪Sorry, I was a little late♪

3
00:00:10,454 --> 00:00:16,882
♪I really want the unconscious longing
to appear faster♪

4
00:00:16,882 --> 00:00:21,362
♪Can I get closer
and hear you say "I do" once more♪

5
00:00:21,362 --> 00:00:25,810
♪Holding hands, the scenery
in midsummer is a new journey♪

6
00:00:25,810 --> 00:00:30,721
♪The chapters of a fairy tale
are performed one after another♪

7
00:00:30,721 --> 00:00:34,770
♪The promised moment
will definitely not be forgotten♪

8
00:00:34,770 --> 00:00:39,305
♪Can I get closer and listen to
the frequency of your heartbeat♪

9
00:00:39,305 --> 00:00:43,602
♪Start the countdown 4321,
a new scenery♪

10
00:00:43,602 --> 00:00:48,367
♪I want to see all the scenes about you♪

11
00:00:48,367 --> 00:00:51,858
♪No need to miss you anymore♪

12
00:00:51,858 --> 00:00:55,538
♪Right by your side♪

13
00:00:57,184 --> 00:01:00,562
=Jin Secretary=

14
00:01:00,562 --> 00:01:03,250
=Episode 22=

15
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:23,133
Boss.

16
00:01:23,333 --> 00:01:27,666
This is the new plan for the new quarter.
Please take a look.

17
00:01:27,766 --> 00:01:30,466
Why are you so formal all of a sudden?

18
00:01:30,533 --> 00:01:32,766
Don't you usually call me Mr. Lan?

19
00:01:32,866 --> 00:01:35,300
Just call me Chen.

20
00:01:35,433 --> 00:01:37,866
Okay, Chen.

21
00:01:50,366 --> 00:01:51,399
You don't work today?

22
00:01:53,100 --> 00:01:56,000
I'm unemployed.
My sister is back to work.

23
00:01:56,866 --> 00:01:58,966
I know a foreign boxing team.

24
00:01:59,100 --> 00:02:02,466
They are looking for a coach.
Are you interested?

25
00:02:02,533 --> 00:02:04,999
Sure, send me the contact information.

26
00:02:16,333 --> 00:02:20,600
If you go abroad, I can't see you then.

27
00:02:30,666 --> 00:02:33,399
I just want a place
where no one knows me.

28
00:02:39,633 --> 00:02:44,000
Oh, don't mention this to my mom.

29
00:02:57,133 --> 00:02:59,466
Hello, Miss Jin.

30
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:13,824
Harder.

31
00:03:14,066 --> 00:03:16,966
Milk tea, hot pot,

32
00:03:17,166 --> 00:03:18,900
and anything you like.

33
00:03:19,333 --> 00:03:21,966
But complete your job first, okay?

34
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:26,333
Please get your things done
as soon as possible.

35
00:03:31,633 --> 00:03:32,992
Harder.

36
00:03:35,866 --> 00:03:38,266
I have checked out past accounts,

37
00:03:38,366 --> 00:03:42,266
some of which are indeed a bit complex.

38
00:03:42,333 --> 00:03:43,999
I'll deal with it
with the finance department.

39
00:03:44,033 --> 00:03:46,666
And here is another issue.

40
00:03:46,733 --> 00:03:50,066
It hasn't caused any loss yet.

41
00:03:50,133 --> 00:03:52,000
That's all for now.

42
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:54,720
Okay.

43
00:03:57,633 --> 00:04:02,166
Miss Jin, why are you so gentle today?

44
00:04:03,666 --> 00:04:05,133
Is it because of last night...?

45
00:04:15,766 --> 00:04:17,333
Mr. Lan, last night...

46
00:04:42,166 --> 00:04:43,648
Sit.

47
00:04:44,133 --> 00:04:47,333
Mr. Lan, I heard
you were investigating me.

48
00:04:58,600 --> 00:05:00,000
Coming.

49
00:05:08,333 --> 00:05:09,833
May I know...?

50
00:05:10,966 --> 00:05:12,200
I am Lan Chen's mother.

51
00:05:15,033 --> 00:05:16,200
You're investigating me?

52
00:05:16,566 --> 00:05:17,866
Yes.

53
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:19,566
Why is that?

54
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:22,766
Don't mind it. I'm just doing my job.

55
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:25,400
Is this your grandfather's idea?

56
00:05:25,400 --> 00:05:28,100
No, it's unrelated to my grandfather.

57
00:05:28,166 --> 00:05:32,266
I just noticed some unclear bills

58
00:05:32,433 --> 00:05:34,866
you recently approved.

59
00:05:34,933 --> 00:05:38,166
Mei Xiangfa is simply too sophisticated.

60
00:05:38,266 --> 00:05:39,833
I was blinded by him.

61
00:05:39,933 --> 00:05:41,466
Humph.

62
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:44,533
You're not a fatuous man.

63
00:05:44,733 --> 00:05:47,933
Or, how can you be the second
largest shareholder and general manager?

64
00:05:47,933 --> 00:05:49,866
People back me up.

65
00:05:52,533 --> 00:05:53,824
Alright.

66
00:05:54,833 --> 00:05:57,766
You prepare
for the press conference tonight.

67
00:05:58,266 --> 00:05:59,456
Also,

68
00:06:01,200 --> 00:06:03,333
my confession thing counts on you.

69
00:06:06,633 --> 00:06:07,566
Please have a seat.

70
00:06:12,633 --> 00:06:14,066
I'll get you some tea.

71
00:06:27,966 --> 00:06:29,233
Please have some tea.

72
00:06:32,333 --> 00:06:34,866
You're also raising children alone.

73
00:06:36,200 --> 00:06:37,200
It's not easy.

74
00:06:38,433 --> 00:06:44,166
My husband died in an accident
when fishing out on the ocean.

75
00:06:45,733 --> 00:06:48,266
Are you also raising children alone?

76
00:06:52,833 --> 00:06:56,899
My husband had a car accident,

77
00:06:56,966 --> 00:06:58,366
and he died on the spot.

78
00:07:00,566 --> 00:07:02,466
Back then,
Gu Qianqian was also in the car.

79
00:07:03,666 --> 00:07:05,999
About Qianqian,

80
00:07:06,166 --> 00:07:08,766
I also feel very sorry.

81
00:07:08,833 --> 00:07:11,600
I didn't expect our group's affairs
to affect you.

82
00:07:13,566 --> 00:07:15,166
Here is a little token of my affection.

83
00:07:17,100 --> 00:07:19,533
I hope your daughter

84
00:07:20,400 --> 00:07:22,433
could stop bothering Lan Chen.

85
00:07:23,333 --> 00:07:25,166
How could I accept this?

86
00:07:25,233 --> 00:07:26,966
Don't look down on us.

87
00:07:30,133 --> 00:07:32,733
You may leave now.

88
00:07:33,266 --> 00:07:34,166
By the way,

89
00:07:37,200 --> 00:07:40,533
regarding the investment
from Lihuai International,

90
00:07:41,400 --> 00:07:42,866
I will also follow up.

91
00:07:43,966 --> 00:07:45,233
I don't want you

92
00:07:45,300 --> 00:07:47,900
to bear such a big pressure alone.

93
00:07:49,200 --> 00:07:51,300
Thank you, Mr. Lan.

94
00:07:51,366 --> 00:07:55,733
However, your mother wants me
to be in charge.

95
00:07:55,733 --> 00:07:57,300
You are so busy.

96
00:07:57,466 --> 00:08:00,000
I'm afraid
you can't spare so much time and energy.

97
00:08:07,492 --> 00:08:12,014
♪I pass through the crowd with you♪

98
00:08:15,044 --> 00:08:20,005
♪As if we have a tacit understanding,
attracting each other♪

99
00:08:23,054 --> 00:08:28,878
♪When the loneliness cracks,
warmth seeps in♪

100
00:08:28,878 --> 00:08:36,348
♪You come with light,
shining into my heart♪

101
00:08:36,348 --> 00:08:39,829
♪Stars fall into my eyes,
and you fall into my heart♪

102
00:08:39,829 --> 00:08:43,950
♪I make a wish foolishly,
but actually, you are the shooting star♪

103
00:08:43,950 --> 00:08:45,646
♪Open my secret♪

104
00:08:45,646 --> 00:08:51,694
♪I hope you find
all the tenderness hidden for you♪

105
00:08:51,694 --> 00:08:55,566
♪Sinking into your love,
I want to sink deeper♪

106
00:08:55,566 --> 00:09:00,072
♪With each breath,
I can feel the sweetness♪

107
00:09:00,072 --> 00:09:08,782
♪Two lonely islands meet,
and it's the gift of fate♪
